task.summary: Add DAO, service interfaces and classes. Separate side bar and dynamically display Categories.
Add model, DAO, service and controller for Product.
Add Jacson for returning JSON to views. Add controllers and request mappings for displaying products.
Add DataTables and JSON request mappings for display products
Add controller, view for displaying product details.
Handle NoHandlerFoundException. Define and handle ProductNotFoundException. Add error page.
Display "Out of Stock" and disable "Add to Cart" buttons for products with 0 quantity.
Add controller, view for add new product or edit existing product.
Add validation before saving a product (name, brand, description, unitPrice, quantity, category).
Add upload and validation for product thumbnail image. Move carousel to top of all pages. Change theme to Yeti.
Add control, view for Admin Portal - Manage Products (list). Handle activate/deactivate products.
Handle edit product/add new product with thumbnail image display on the form. Refactor FileUploadUtility and AdminController to reduce coupling.
Change page layout to col-sm-12. Add activation checkbox for Edit/Add Product form
Add model and DAO for User, Address and Cart. Add config for Web Flow and flows for registering new user.
Change scan packages to base class.
